---
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-[#fbfaf7]">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        Common questions.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
        Everything you need to know about working with Local Leader.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">
          How long until I see results?
          <span class="transition duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Most clients see initial movement in their Maps rankings within the first 30-45 days. Significant organic traffic growth and consistent lead generation typically compound between months 3 and 6 as your authority builds.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">
          Do I need to spend money on ads?
          <span class="transition duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          No. Our entire system is built around organic visibility (Local SEO and Google Maps). Once you rank organically, those clicks are free. You never have to pay Google for a lead again.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">
          What if I'm already with another SEO company?
          <span class="transition duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We can seamlessly take over your campaign. In fact, many of our best clients came to us after being burned by generic agencies. We'll audit what they've done, fix any issues, and accelerate your growth.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">
          Is there a lock-in contract?
          <span class="transition duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We ask for an initial 3-month commitment because SEO takes time to build momentum. After that, we operate purely on a month-to-month basis. We keep you by delivering results, not with legal red tape.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">
          What exactly do I get for $500/month?
          <span class="transition duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          You get our complete Local Leader system: Full Google Business Profile management, 50+ directory citations, our automated 5-star review engine, ongoing on-page SEO for your website, and transparent monthly reporting.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">
          How is this different from other SEO companies?
          <span class="transition duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We don't do generic marketing. We specialise exclusively in local service businesses in Australia. We don't just focus on website traffic; we focus on dominating the Map Pack and building your review profile, because that's what actually makes the phone ring.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
